          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Honoring Investments in Recruiting and Employing American Military Veterans Act of 2015 or the HIRE Vets Act</strong></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Labor to establish a HIRE Vets Medallion Program to solicit voluntary information from employers for purposes of recognizing, by the award of a HIRE Vets Medallion, verified efforts by these employers to: (1) recruit, employ, and retain veterans; and (2) provide community and charitable services supporting the veteran community. </p>]]></text>
